14 SECTION 4. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 852 of Title 17, unless there is
16 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 On or before January 1, 2026, the Corporation Commission, in
18 consultation with the Oklahoma Agrivoltaics Advisory Committee,
19 shall prepare a report and submit to the Legislature. The report
20 shall include, but shall not be limited to:
21 1. A list and explanation of existing tools and government
22 initiatives designed to help in the siting and construction of
23 renewable energy projects and transmission systems in a manner
