15 SECTION 5. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 853 of Title 17, unless there is
17 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving fund
19 for the Corporation Commission, to be designated the "Oklahoma
20 Agrivoltaics Cash Revolving Fund". The fund shall be a continuing
21 fund, not subject to fiscal year limitations, and shall consist of
22 all monies designated for deposit to said fund, including any money
23 received as gifts, grants, or other contributions from public or
24 private sources. All monies accruing to the credit of said fund are
Req. No. 11595 Page 6

1 here by appropriated and may be budgeted and shall be expended by the
2 Corporation Commission for the purposes of carrying out the
3 provisions of the Oklahoma Agrivoltaics Act. Expenditures from said
4 fund shall be made upon warrants issued by the State Treasurer
